  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.media.JingleMediaSession

  • public class RawMediaSession
extends org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingle.media.JingleMediaSession
    This RawMediaSession extends the JingleMediaSession to create a session (it decides itself whether this RawMediaSession should transmit or receive data)
